  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Farming & Supermarket Simulator\" is a delightful simulation game where you build a farm, grow organic products, feed your animals, and expand your business by selling your products in your supermarket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow, Harvest, Use</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make the best use of your harvested products: either fill the supermarket shelves or use them as feed for your animals. The choice is yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> <br> </strong>Feed and Collect</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>Feed your animals and reap the rewards! Feed your chicken a tomato, collect fresh eggs, and enjoy the fruits of your labor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Invest in Machines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your production by purchasing machines! Process your harvested goods to produce valuable items for your supermarket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cashier</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quickly scan items, accept payments in cash or credit, and ensure your customers leave happy with their shopping experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>Work Smart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quickly move your product crates to the market, fill the shelves, and meet your customers' demands!<strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Supermarket Expansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your supermarket with the money you earn! More space, more products, and more customers mean more sales. Strategically organize your shelves and highlight popular products.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farm Expansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think your farm is too small? Then expand it further. Open more farmland, purchase new machines, and increase animal diversity to grow your farm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Farming & Supermarket Simulator\" will show you how enjoyable managing both a farm and a supermarket can be. Set your strategy, grow step by step, and achieve success. Enjoy this detailed and delightful gaming experience and become the owner of a large farm and supermarket chain!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Farming & Supermarket Simulator\" is a delightful simulation game where you build a farm, grow organic products, feed your animals, and expand your business by selling your products in your supermarket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Grow, Harvest, Use</h2></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make the best use of your harvested products: either fill the supermarket shelves or use them as feed for your animals. The choice is yours!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/712613ddd0613d6588c7d221a2dcafdb.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong> <br> </strong>Feed and Collect</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong>Feed your animals and reap the rewards! Feed your chicken a tomato, collect fresh eggs, and enjoy the fruits of your labor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/8ba366275e2d3ed672f2876474fefe21.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Invest in Machines</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expand your production by purchasing machines! Process your harvested goods to produce valuable items for your supermarket.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/fcbec3284c7bdcbe05564a2d1795886c.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cashier</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quickly scan items, accept payments in cash or credit, and ensure your customers leave happy with their shopping experience!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/69d284bb826c99a29b9c6b9578aae2fd.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><br>Work Smart</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quickly move your product crates to the market, fill the shelves, and meet your customers' demands!<strong></strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/704cb1bf3819e2accc9583a58467139f.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Supermarket Expansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Grow your supermarket with the money you earn! More space, more products, and more customers mean more sales. Strategically organize your shelves and highlight popular products.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.poster.avif?t=1759347912\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.webm?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070880/extras/70425e5b910ef9896f812efc6b341a2f.mp4?t=1759347912\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Farm Expansion</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Think your farm is too small? Then expand it further. Open more farmland, purchase new machines, and increase animal diversity to grow your farm. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Farming & Supermarket Simulator\" will show you how enjoyable managing both a farm and a supermarket can be. Set your strategy, grow step by step, and achieve success. Enjoy this detailed and delightful gaming experience and become the owner of a large farm and supermarket chain!</p>",
